hadiths[170]{hadithnumber,text}:
3398,"abu-Muawiya ne hamein Aamash se khabar di, unhon-ne Ibrahim se, unhon-ne Alqama se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : main Mina mein Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath paidal chal raha tha ke Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) se unki mulaqat hui, wo khadey ho kar unse baatein karne lagey. saiyedna Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ne unse kaha : abu-Abdur-Rehman ! kya ham kisi naujawan ladki se aap ki shadi na kara dein, shayad wo aapko aap ka wahi zamana yad kara de jo guzar chuka hai? kaha : to Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : agar aap ne ye baat kahi hai to (is se pahley) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ham se farmaya tha : aey jawaanon ke giroh ! tum mein se jo koi shadi ki istitaat rakhta ho wo shadi kar ley , ye nigah ko zyada jhukaney wali aur sharmgah ki zyada hifazat karne wali hai aur jo istitaat nahi rakhta to wo rozey ko lazim kar ley , ye uske liye khahish ko qaabu mein karne ka zaria hai."
3399,"Jarir ne hamein Aamash se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Ibrahim se, unhon-ne Alqama se riwayat ki, kaha : main Mina mein Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath paidal chal raha tha ke Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) unse miley to unhon-ne kaha : abu-Abdur-Rehman ! ( mere saath) aaein. kaha : wo unhein tanhai mein ley gaey. jab Abdullah (bin Masood) (Raziallahu anhu) ne dekha ke unhein us ( tanhai ( ki zarurat nahi, to unhon-ne mujhey bula liya. (kaha :) Alqama aa jao! main aa gaya, to saiyedna Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ne unse kaha : abu-Abdur-Rehman! kya ham kisi kunwari ladki se aap ki shadi na kara dein, shayad ye aap ke dil ki usi kaifiyat ko lota de jo aap (ahad jawani) mein mehsus kartey they? to Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne jawab diya : agar aap ne ye baat kahi hai. phir abu-Muawia ki hadis ki tarah bayan kya."
3400,"abu-Muawia ne hamein Aamash se hadis sunai, unhon-ne Umara-bin-Umair se, unhon-ne Abdur-Rehman-bin-Yazeed se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah (bin-Masood ( (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ham se farmaya : aey jawaanon ki jamat ! tum mein se jo shadi karne ki istitaat rakhta ho wo shadi kar ley. ye nigahon ko jhukaaney aur sharmgah ki hifazat karne mein (doosri chizon ki nisbat ( badh kar hai. aur jo istitaat na paaey , wo khud par rozey ko lazim kar ley , ye uske liye uski khahish ko qata' karne wala hai."
3401,"Jarir ne hamein Aamash se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Umara-bin-Umair se, unhon-ne Abdur-Rehman-bin-Yazeed (bin-Qis ( se riwayat ki, kaha : main, mere chacha Alqama (bin-Qais (aur ( mere bhai ( Aswad (bin-Yazeed-bin-Qais (Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir huey. kaha : main un dinon jawan tha. unhon-ne aik hadis bayan ki, mujhey yun lagta hai ke wo unhon-ne meri wjah se bayan ki. unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ( aagey ( abu-Muawia ki hadis ki tarah hai. aur (ye ( izafa kiya, kaha : iske baad maine zyada arsa twaqquf kiye baghair shadi kar li."
3402,"Wakee ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Aamash ne baqi bachi pichhli sanad ke sath Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, ( Abdur-Rehman-bin-Yazeed ne) kaha : ham unki khidmat mein hazir huey, main sabse kam Umr tha, aagey unhi ki hadis ki tarah hai, ( magar ( unhon-ne ye nahi kaha : iske baad maine zyada arsa twaqquf kiye baghair shadi kar li."
3403,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sahaba mein se kuchh logon ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki paak beeviyon se aap ki tanhai ke ma'moolaat ke barey mein sawal kiya. phir unmein se kisi ne kaha : main aurton se shadi nahi karunga, kisi ne kaha : main gosht nahi khaaunga , aur kisi ne kaha : main bistar par nahi soun ga. ( aapko pata chala ( to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Allah ki hamd ki, uski sana bayan ki aur farmaya : logon ka kya haal hai? unhon-ne is-is tarah se kaha hai. lekin main to Namaz padhta hon aur aaraam bhi karta hun, rozey rakhta hun aur iftaar bhi karta hun aur aurton se nikah bhi karta hun, jisne meri sunnat se raghbat (dilchaspi) hata li wo mujh se nahi."
3404,"Mamar ne Zohri se, unhon-ne Saeed-bin-Musaiyab se aur unhon-ne Sad-bin-abi-Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Usman-bin-maz'oon (Raziallahu anhu) ki) taraf se) nikah ko tark karke ibadat mein mashghooliyat (ke iraadey ( ko mustarad farma diya. agar aap unhein ijazat de detey to ham sab khud ko khassi kar letey."
3405,"Ibrahim-bin-Sad ne hamein ibne-Shahab Zohri se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Saeed-bin-Musaiyab se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha ke maine Sad se suna wo keh rahe they ki Usman-bin-maz'oon (Raziallahu anhu) ‌ ‌ ke tark nikah ko) iraadey ko) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf se radd kar diya gaya, agar unhein ijazat mil jati to ham sab khassi ho jatey."
3406,"Uqail ne ibne-Shahab se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Saeed-bin-Musaiyab ne khabar di ke unhon-ne Sad-bin-abi-Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they : Usman-bin-maz'oon (Raziallahu anhu) ne irada kya ke wo ( ibadat ke liye nikah aur ghardaarii se) alag ho jayen to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein mana farma diya, agar aap unhein iski ijazat de detey to ham sab khassi ho jatey."
3407,"Hisham-bin-abi-Abdullah ne abu-Zubair se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke aik aurat par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki nazar pad gaee to aap apni ahliya Hazrat Zenab (Raziallahu anha) ke paas aaey. wo apne liye aik chamdey ko rang rahi thin, aap ne (ghar mein) apni zarurat poori farmai. phir apne sahaba ki taraf tashrif le gaey, aur farmaya : bila shubah ( fitney mein dalney ke hawale se) aurat shaitan ki sura mein samney aati hai aur shaitan hi ki sura mein mudkar wapas jati hai. tum mein se koi jab kisi aurat ko dekhey to wo apni biwi ke paas aa jaey, bila shubah ye cheez us khahish ko hata degi jo iske dil main ( paida hui ( hai."
3408,"harab-bin-abu-Aaliya ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein abu-Zubair ne Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki nazar aik aurat par pad gaee. aagey usi ki tarah bayan kiya, albatta unhon-ne kaha : Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni biwi Zenab (Raziallahu anha) ke paas aaey jabke wo chamdey ko rang rahi thin aur ye nahi kaha : wo shaitan ki sura mein wapas aa jati hai."
3409,"Maaqil ne abu-Zubair se riwayat ki, kaha : Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : maine Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna : jab tum mein se kisi ko , koi aurat achi lagey, aur uske dil mein jaey to wo apni biwi ka rukh karey aur us se sohbat karey, bila shubah ye (amal (us kaifiyat ko door kar dega jo iske dil main ( paida hui ( hai."
3410,"Muhammad-bin-Abdullah-bin-Numair Hamdani ne kaha : mere walid ne aur Wakee aur ibne-Bishr ne hamein Ismail se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Qais se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Abdullah (bin-Masood) (Raziallahu anhu) ko kehtey huey suna : ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath jihad kartey they aur hamarey paas auratein nahi hoti thin. to ham ne (aap se) malum kiya : kya ham khassi na ho jayen? aap ne hamein is se mana farma diya. phir aap ne hamein rukhsat di ke ham kisi aurat se aik kapdey (ya zarurat ki kisi aur cheez (ke iwaz muqarrara waqt tak nikah kar lein, phir Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne (ye aayat ( tilawat ki : aey logo jo eman laey ! wo pakeeza cheezein haram mat thehrao jo Allah ne tumharey liye halal ki hain aur had se na badho, be-shak Allah Taala had se badhney walon ko pasand nahi karta."
3411,"Jarir ne Ismail-bin-abi-Khalid se isi sanad ke sath , usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki aur kaha : phir unhon-ne hamarey samney ye aayat padhi. unhon-ne ( naam lekar ( Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne padhi nahi kaha."
3412,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba ne kaha : hamein Wakee ne Ismail se isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki, aur kaha : ham sab naujawaan they, to ham ne kaha : aey Allah ke rasool ! kya ham khassi na ho jayen? aur unhon-ne ( نغزو ( ) ham jihad kartey they) ke alfaz nahi kahey ."
3413,"Shoba ne hamein Amr-bin-Dinar se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hasan-bin- Muhammad se suna, wo Jabir-bin-Abdullah aur Salma-bin-Akwa (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan kar rahe they, un donon ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka aik manadi karne wala hamarey paas aaya aur elaan kya : bila shubah Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne tumhen istimtaa (fayda uthaney), yani aurton se (nikah) mutaa karne ki ijazat di hai"
3414,"Rooh bin-Qasim ne hamein Amr-bin-Dinar se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hasan-bin- Muhammad se, unhon-ne Salma-bin-Akwa aur Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hamarey paas aaey ( elaan ki sura mein aap ka paigham aaya (aur hamein mutaa ki ijazat di."
3415,"Ata ne kaha : Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) Umerey ke liye aaey to ham unki rihaaish gaah par unki khidmat mein hazir huey, logon ne unse mukhtalif chizon ke barey mein poochha, phir logon ne mutaa ka tazkira kya to unhon-ne kaha : haan, ham ne Rasulullah (sl), Abu-Bakar aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke ahad mein mutaa kya."
3416,"mujhey abu-Zubair ne khabar di, kaha : maine Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they : ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke daur mein aik muththi khajoor aur aatey ke iwaz chand dinon ke liye mutaa kartey they, yahan tak ke Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne Amr-bin-Hurais ke waqiey (ke doran) mein us se mana kar diya."
3417,"abu-Nazara se riwayat hai, kaha : main Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas tha ke unke paas aik aaney wala ( mulaqati) aaya aur kehney laga : Hazrat Ibne-Abbas aur ibne-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) ne donon muton (hajje-tamatto aur nikahe-mutaa) ke barey mein ikhtilaf kya hai. to Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ahad mein wo donon kaam kiye, phir Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne hamein un donon se mana kar diya, phir ham ne dobara unka rukh nahi kya."
3418,"Ayas bin Salma ne apne walid (Salma-bin-Akwa (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne autas ke saal teen din mutey ki ijazat di, phir us se mana farma diya."
3419,"Leis ne hamein Rabe bin sabra Johni se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne apne walid sabra (bin Mabad Johni (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein ( nikah ( mutaa ki ijazat di. main aur aik aadmi banu-Aamir ki aik aurat ke paas gaey, wo jawan aur lambi gardan wali khoobsurat oontni jaisi thi, ham ne khud ko uske samney pesh kya to usne kaha : kya doge? maine kaha : apni chadar aur mere sathi ne bhi kaha : apni chadar. mere sathi ki chadar meri chadar se behtar thi, aur main is se zyada jawan tha. jab wo mere sathi ki chadar ki taraf dekhti to wo usey achi lagti aur jab wo meri taraf dekhti to main uske dil ko bhata, phir us ne (mujh se) kaha : tum aur tumhari chadar hi mere liye kafi hai. iske baad main teen din uske sath raha, phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jis kisi ke paas un aurton mein se, jin se wo mutaa karta hai, koi (aurat) ho, to wo uska rasta chhod de."
3420,"Bashar-bin-Mufazzal ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Umara-bin-Ghaziya ne Rabe bin sabra se hadis bayan ki ke unke walid ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath jange-fatah Makka mein shirkat ki, kaha : ham ne wahan pandarah roz .) alag alag din aur raatein ginin to) tees shab w roz. qiyam kya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein aurton se mutaa karne ki ijazat de di, chunanche main aur meri qaum ka aik aadmi nikley. mujhey husn main is par tarjeeh hasil thi aur wo taqriban bad-soorat tha. ham donon mein se har aik ke paas chadar thi, meri chadar puraani thi aur mere chacha zaad ki chadar nai (aur) mulaaim thi, yahan tak ke jab ham Makka ke nashebi (nichley) ilaaqey mein ya uske oopri ilaaqey mein pahunchey to hamari mulaqat lambi gardan wali jawan aur khoobsurat ontni jaisi aurat se hui, ham ne kaha : kya tum chahti ho ke ham mein se koi aik tumharey sath mutaa karey? usne kaha : tum donon kya kharch karogey? is par ham mein se har aik ne apni-apni chadar (uske samney) phaila di, is par us ne donon aadmiyon ko dekhna shuru kar diya aur mera sathi usko dekhney laga aur uske pahlu par nazrein gaad din aur kehney laga : uski chadar puraani hai aur meri chadar nai aur mulaaim hai. is par wo kehney lagi : uski chadar mein bhi koi kharabi nahi. teen baar ya 2 baar ye baat hui. phir maine us se mutaa kar liya aur phir main iske haan se (us waqt tak) na nikla, yahan tak ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey (mutaa ko) haram qarar de diya."
3421,"hamein Wuhaib ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Umara bin ghaziya ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : Rabe bin sabra Johni ne apne walid se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : fateh Makka ke saal ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Makka ki taraf nikley, aagey Bishr ki hadis ki tarah bayan kya aur ye izafa kya is aurat ne kaha : kya ye (mutaa) jaaiz hai? aur usi (riwaayat ( mein hai : ( mere sathi ne) kaha : uski chadar puraani bosida hai."
3422,"Abdullah-bin-Numair ne kaha : hamein Abdul-Azeez bin umr ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : mujhey Rabe bin sabra Johni ne hadis sunai ke unke walid ne unhein hadis bayan ki ke wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath they, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : logo ! be-shak maine tumhen aurton se mutaa karne ki ijazat di thi, aur bila shubah ab Allah Taala ne usey qiyamat ke din tak ke liye haram kar diya hai, isliye jis kisi ke paas un aurton mein se koi ( aurat maujood (ho to wo iska rasta chhod de, aur jo kuchh tum logon ne unhein diya hai is mein se koi cheez ( wapas ( mat lo."
3423,"Abda bin Sulaiman ne Abdul-Azeez bin umr se isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki, kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko hajre-Aswad aur (Baitullah ke) darwazey ke darmyan khadey huey dekha, aur aap farma rahe they. ( aagey ( ibne-Numair ki hadis ki tarah hai"
3424,"Abdul-Malik bin Rabe bin sabra Johni ne apne walid ke hawale se apne dada ( sabra bin Mabad (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat ki, kaha : fateh Makka ke saal jab ham Makka mein dakhil huey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein ( nikah ( mutaa (ke jawaz (ka hukm diya, phir abhi ham wahan se nikley na they ke aap ne hamein us se mana farma diya."
3425,"Abdul-Azeez bin Rabe bin sabra bin Mabad ne kaha : maine apne walid Rabe bin sabra se suna, wo apne walid sabra bin Mabad (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan kar rahe they ke fateh Makka ke saal Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne sathiyon ko aurton ke sath mutaa kar leney ka hukm diya. main aur banu-Sulaim mein se mera aik sathi nikley, yahan tak ke ham ne banu-Aamir ki aik jawan ladki ko paya , wo aik jawan aur khoobsurat lambi gardan wali ontni ki tarah thi. ham ne usey nikah ( mutaa (ka paigham diya, aur uske samney apni chaadrein pesh kin, wo ghaur se dekhney lagi, mujhey mere sathi se zyada khoobsurat paati aur mere sathi ki chadar ko meri chadar se behtar dekhti, iske baad us ne ghadi bhar apne dil se mashwara kya, phir usne mujhey mere sathi par fauqiyat di, phir ye auratein teen din tak hamarey sath rahin, phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein unko alehda karne ka hukm diya."
3426,"Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne hamein Zohri se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Rabe bin Sabra se aur unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne nikahe-mutaa se mana farma diya."
3427,"Mamar ne Zohri se, unhon-ne Rabe bin sabra se, unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne fateh Makka ke) dinon mein se aik ( din aurton ke sath ( nikah ( mutaa karne se mana farma diya."
3428,"Saleh se riwayat hai, kaha : hamein ibne-Shahab ne Rabe bin sabra Johni se khabar di, unhon-ne apne walid ( sabra (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne unko bataya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne fateh Makka ke zamaney mein aurton se mutaa karne se mana farma diya tha, aur ye ke unke walid ( sabra ( ne (apne sathi ke saath) 2 surkh chaadrein pesh kartey huey nikahe-mutaa kya tha."
3429,"mujhey Yunus ne khabar di ke ibne-Shahab ne kaha : mujhey Urwa-bin-Zubair ne khabar di ke Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) Makka mein khadey huey, aur kaha : bila shubah kuchh log hain, Allah ne unke dilon ko bhi andha kar diya hai jis tarah unki aankhon ko andha kya hai. wo logon ko mutaa (ke jawaz (ka fatwa detey hain, wo aik aadmi (Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu)) par aitiraz kar rahe they, is par unhon-ne unko pukara aur kaha : tum be adab, kam-faham (samajh) ho, meri umr ki qasam! bila shubah imamul-muttaqeen ke daur main (nikah) mutaa kya jata tha. unki murad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se thi. to ibne-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) ne unse kaha : tum khud apne sath iska tajriba kar) dekho ), b-khuda! agar tum ne ye kaam kya to main tumharey ( hi un ( pattharon se ( jinke tum mustahiq hogey ( tumhen rajm (sangsaar) karunga . ibne-Shahab ne kaha : mujhey Khalid-bin muhajir bin saif Allah ne khabar di ke is beech mein jab wo un sahib (ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu)) ke paas baithey huey they, aik aadmi unke paas aaya aur mutaa ke barey mein unse fatwa maanga to unhon-ne usey us (ke jawaz (ka hukm diya. is par ibne-abi Umra Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) ne unse kaha : thahriye ! unhon-ne kaha : kya hua? Allah ki qism ! maine imamul-muttaqeen (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ahad mein kya hai. ibne-abi Umra (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : bila shubah ye ( aisa kaam hai ke) ibtadaaey Islam mein aisey shakhs ke liye jo ( halaat ki bina par) uske liye majbur kar diya gaya ho, uski rukhsat thi jis tarah ( majburi mein) murdar , khoon aur Sura ke gosht (ke liye) hai, phir Allah Taala ne apne Deen ko mohkam kya aur us se mana farma diya. ibne-Shahab ne kaha : mujhey Rabe bin sabra Johni ne bataya ke unke walid ne kaha : maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamaney mein banu-Aamir ki aik aurat se 2 surkh chaadaron (ki pesh kash! ( par mutaa kya tha, phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein mutaa se mana farma diya. ibne-Shahab ne kaha : maine Rabe bin sabra se suna, wo yahi hadis Umar-bin Abdul-Azeez se bayan kar rahe they aur main (is majlis mein) betha hua tha."
3430,"hamein Maaqil ne ibne-abi abla se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Umar-bin Abdul-Azeez se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Rabe bin sabra Johni ne apne walid se hadis bayan ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mutaa se roka aur farmaya : khabardaar ! ye tumharey aaj ke din se qiyamat ke din tak ke liye haram hai aur jisne ( mutaa ke badaley) koi cheez di ho wo usey wapas na ley."
3431,"Yahya-bin-Yahya ne kaha : maine Imam Malik ke samney qirat ki, unhon-ne ibne-Shahab se, unhon-ne Muhammad-bin Ali ( ibn-Hanfiya (ke donon beton Abdullah aur Hasan se, un donon ne apne walid se, aur unhon-ne Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khaibar ke din aurton ke sath mutaa karne aur paaltu gadhon ka gosht khaney se mana farma diya tha."
3432,"hamein Abdullah-bin Muhammad-bin Asma Zubai ne hadis sunai, kaha : hamein Juweriya (bin Asma bin Ubaid Zubai ( ne Imam Malik (Rehmatullahi-alaih) Mina se isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki aur kaha : unhon ( Muhammad-bin Ali ( ne Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo falan (Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu)) se keh rahe they : tum hairat mein padey huey (haqiqat se be khabar ( shakhs ho. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mana farma diya tha. padhi. aagey Yahya-bin-Yahya ki Imam Malik (Rehmatullahi-alaih) Mina se riwayat ki hui hadis ki tarah hai."
3433,"Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne hamein Zohri se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Muhammad-bin Ali ( ibn-Hanfiya (ke donon beton Hasan aur Abdullah se, un donon ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khaibar ke din ( nikah ( mutaa aur paaltu gadhon ke gosht se mana farma diya tha."
3434,"Ubaidullah ne ibne-Shahab se, unhon-ne Muhammad-bin-Ali se ke donon beton Hasan aur Abdullah se, un donon ne apne walid ( Muhammad ibn-Hanfiya) se, aur unhon-ne (apne walid) Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo aurton se mutaa karne ke barey mein (fatwa dene mein) narmi se kaam letey hain, unhon-ne kaha : Ibne-Abbas ! thehariye! bila shubah Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khaibar ke din us se aur paaltu gadhon ke gosht se mana farma diya tha."
3435,"Yunus ne mujhey ibne-Shahab se khabar di, unhon-ne Muhammad-bin Ali-bin abi-Talib ke beton Hasan aur Abdullah se (aur ( un donon ne apne walid (Muhammad-bin Ali ibn-Hanfiya) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Ali-bin abi-Talib (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se keh rahe they : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khaibar ke din aurton ke sath mutaa karne aur paaltu gadhon ke gosht khaney se mana farma diya tha."
3436,"Aaraj ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kisi aurat aur uski phuphi ko, aur kisi aurat aur uski khala ko (nikah mein) ikattha na kya jaey."
3437,Irak-bin-Malik ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne char aurton ke barey mein mana farmaya ke unko (nikah mein aapasi) jama kya jaey : aurat aur uski phoophi (ya) aurat aur uski khala.
3438,"Abdur-Rehman bin Abdul-Azeez ne ibne-Shahab se khabar di, unhon-ne Qabisa bin zuweb se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : bhai ki beti par phoophi ko na biyaha jaey aur na khala ke hotey huey bhanji se nikah kya jaey. (asl maqsud yahi hai ke ye ikatthi aik shakhs ke nikah mein na aaein."
3439,"Yunus ne mujhey ibne-Shahab se khabar di, kaha : mujhey Qabisa bin zuweb Kabi ne khabar di ke unhon-ne saiyedna Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se suna wo keh rahe they : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mana farmaya ke koi shakhs kisi aurat aur uski phuphi ko aur kisi aurat aur uski khala ko (apne nikah mein aik saath) jama kare. ibne-Shahab ne kaha : ham us ( mankooha aurat (ke walid ki khala aur walid ki phuphi ko bhi usi haisiyat mein dekhtey hain."
3440,"Hisham ne hamein Yahya se hadis bayan ki ke unhon ( Yahya ( ne un ( Hisham ( ki taraf abu-Salma se (apni ( riwayat ki hui hadis likh kar bheji ke Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kisi aurat se uski phuphi aur uski khala ki maujoodgii mein nikah na kya jaey."
3441,"Sheban ne Yahya se riwayat ki, kaha : mujhey abu-Salma ne hadis bayan ki ke unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se suna wo keh rahe they, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, ( aagey ( usi ki tarah hai."
3442,"Hisham ne Muhammad-bin Sirin se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : koi aadmi apne bhai ke paighame-nikah par (apne) nikah ka paigham na de, aur na apne bhai ke saudey par Sauda karey, aur na kisi aurat se uski phuphi aur khala ki maujudgi mein nikah kya jaey aur na koi aurat apni ( musalman ( behan ki talaaq ka mutalba karey taake uski plate ko (apne liye) undel ley. usey ( pehli biwi ki talaaq ka mutalba kiye baghair ( nikah kar lena chahiye, baat yahi hai ke jo Allah ne uske liye likha hua hai wahi iska hai."
3443,"Daawood-bin-abi-Hind ne Ibne-Sirin se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mana farmaya ke kisi aurat ke sath , uski phuphi ya uski khala ke) nikah mein) hotey huey, nikah kya jaey aur us se ke koi aurat apni behan ki talaaq ka mutalba karey taake jo uski plate mein hai, wo ( usey apne liye) undel ley. bila shubah izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ( khud ( usko rizq dene wala hai."
3444,"Shoba ne Amr-bin-Dinar se, unhon-ne abu-Salma se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mana farmaya ke kisi aurat aur uski phuphi ko aur kisi aurat aur uski khala ko (eik mard ke nikah mein) jama kya jaey."
3445,Warqa ne Amr-bin-Dinar se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki.
3446,"Imam Malik ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Nubaih bin Wahab se riwayat ki ke Umar-bin Ubaidullah (bin Mamar Johni ( ne irada kya ke apne betey Talha bin umr ki shadi Sheba bin Juber (bin Usman Johni ( ki beti se kar dein, to unhon-ne Aban bin Usman ki taraf paigham bheja ke wo bhi aaein, wo ameerul-hajj bhi they. Aban ne kaha : maine Hazrat Usman-bin-Affan (Raziallahu anhu) se suna wo keh rahe they : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : (mohrim (ehraam walaa shakhs)) na ( khud ( nikah karey aur na uska nikah karaya jaey aur na wo nikah ka paigham bhejey."
3447,"Ayub ne Naafe se riwayat ki, kaha : mujhey Nubaih bin Wahab ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : mujhey Umar-bin Ubaidullah bin Mamar ne bhejaa. wo Sheba (bin Juber (bin Usman ki beti ke liye apne betey ke nikah ka paigham bhej rahe they, to mujhey unhon-ne Aban bin Usman ki taraf bheja aur wo ameere-hajj they, unhon-ne kaha : kya main usey ( umr ko) aik baddoo ( jaisa kaam kartey ( nahi dekh raha ? jo shakhs haalate-ehram mein ho wo na nikah karta hai na ( kisi ka ( nikah karata hai. hamein Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ne is baat ki khabar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se di thi."
3448,"Matar aur Yala bin-Hakim ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Nubaih-bin-Wahab se, unhon-ne Aban bin Usman se, unhon-ne Usman-bin-Affan (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jo shakhs haalate-ehram mein ho, wo na nikah karey na nikah kiraaey aur na nikah ka paigham bhejey."
3449,"Ayub bin-Musa ne Nubaih-bin-Wahab se, unhon-ne Aban bin Usman se, unhon-ne Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, wo us (ki sanad) ko Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tak pahunchaatey they ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : mohrim (ehraam walaa shakhs) ( jisne ehram baandh rakha ho wo ( nikah karey na nikah ka paigham bhejey"
3450,"Saeed bin abu-Hilaal ne mujhey Nubaih bin Wahab se hadis bayan ki ke Umar-bin Ubaidullah bin Mamar ne irada kya ke Haj (ke dinon) mein apne betey Talha ka nikah Sheba bin Juber ki beti se karein, Aban bin Usman un dinon Haj ke ameer they. to unhon-ne Aban ki taraf paigham bheja ke maine irada kya hai ke Talha bin umr ka nikah kar dun aur main chahta hun ke aap bhi usmein Sharik hon to Aban ne unhein jawab diya : kya mujhey tum aik akkhad iraqi jaisey dikhai nahi de rahe ! bila shubah maine Hazrat Usman-bin-Affan (Raziallahu anhu) ko kehtey huey suna ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : mohrim (jo shakhs haalat ehram mein ho wo ( kisi ka nikah na kiraaey"
3451,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba, ibne-Numair aur Ishaq Hanzali sab ne Sufiyan-bin-Uena se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Amr-bin-Dinar se, unhon-ne abu-Shasha se riwayat ki ke Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein khabar di ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) se nikah kya to aap ehram mein they. ibne-Numair ne ye izafa kya : maine ye hadis Zohri ko sunai to unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Yazeed bin Asamm ne khabar di ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne un (Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ( se us haalat mein nikah kya jabke aap ehram ke baghair they."
3452,"Dawud bin Abdur-Rehman ne hamein Amr-bin-Dinar se khabar di, unhon-ne abu-Shasha Jaabir bin Zaid se, unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) se nikah kya jabke aap haalate ehram mein they."
3453,"Yazeed bin Asamm se riwayat hai, kaha : mujhey Hazrat Memuna binte- Haris (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis bayan ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse us haalat mein nikah kya ke aap ehram ke baghair they. ( Yazeed bin Asamm ne) kaha : wo meri bhi khala thin aur Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ki bhi khala thin."
3454,"Leis ne hamein Naafe se khabar di, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum mein se koi shakhs kisi doosrey ke saudey par Sauda na karey aur na tum mein se koi kisi (aur) ke paigham nikah par nikah ka paigham bhejey."
3455,"Yahya ne hamein Ubaidullah se hadis bayan ki, kaha : mujhey Naafe ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se khabar di, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : koi aadmi apne bhai ke saudey par saudaa na karey aur na apne bhai ke paighame-nikah par paigham bhejey siwaey-iske ke wo usey ijazat de."
3456,Ali-bin-Mus-hir ne Ubaidullah se isi sanad ke sath yahi hadis bayan ki.
3457,Ayub ne Naafe se isi sanad ke sath yahi hadis bayan ki.
3458,"Amr Nafiz, Zuhair-bin-Harab aur ibne-abi-Umar ne hadis bayan ki. Zuhair ne kaha : Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne hamein Zohri se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Saeed-bin-Musaiyab se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is baat se mana farmaya ke koi shehri kisi dehati ke liye Sauda bechey ya log (kharidari ki niyat ke baghair) badh chadh kar qeemat lagaaein ya koi aadmi apne bhai ke paighame-nikah par nikah ka paigham bhejey, ya koi aadmi apne bhai ke saudey par Sauda kare. aur na hi koi aurat (is gharaz se) apni behan ki talaaq ka mutalba karey ke jo kuchh iske bartan mein hai ya uski plate mein hai wo usey (apne liye) undel ley. Amr ne apni hadis mein ye izafa kya : aur na koi aadmi apne bhai ke kiye janey waley saudey par saudaa bazi kare."
3459,"Yunus ne mujhey ibne-Shahab se khabar di, kaha : mujhey Saeed-bin-Musaiyab ne hadis bayan ki ke Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum ( kharidney ki niyat ke baghair ( qeemat na badhaao aur na koi aadmi apne bhai ke saudey par Sauda karey aur na koi shehri kisi dehati ke liye Sauda karey aur na koi aadmi apne bhai ke paighame-nikah par nikah ka paigham bhejey aur na koi aurat dusri aurat ki talaaq ka mutalba karey taake jo kuchh iske bartan mein hai wo usey (apne liye) undel ley."
3460,"Mamar ne Zohri se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki, albatta Mamar ki hadis mein hai : aur na koi aadmi apne bhai ke saudey par izafe (ki pesh kash!) kare."
3461,"Alaa ke walid ( Abdur-Rehman bin Yaqoob ( ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : koi musalman kisi musalman ke saudey par Sauda na karey, aur na uske paighame-nikah par nikah ka paigham bhejey."
3462,"Ahmed bin Ibrahim Dorqi ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : ham se Shoba ne Alaa (bin Abdur-Rehman Johni) aur Suhel (bin abi Saleh samaan madni) se, unhon-ne apne apney walid se, un donon ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se (yahi hadis) riwayat ki."
3463,"hamein Muhammad-bin-Musanna ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Abdus-Samad ne hadis sunai, kaha : hamein Shoba ne Aamash se, unhon-ne Abu-Saleh se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki magar unhon-ne kaha : apne bhai ke saudey par aur apne bhai ke paigham nikah par. (riwaayat : 3461 mein musalman ke alfaz hain. ("
3464,"Abdur-Rehman bin Shimasa se riwayat hai ke unhon-ne member par se Hazrat Aqba-bin-Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : momin doosrey momin ka bhai hai, kisi momin ke liye halal nahi ke wo apne bhai ke saudey par Sauda karey aur na apne bhai ke paighame-nikah par nikah ka paigham bhejey, yahan tak ke wo (khud usey) chhod de."
3465,"Imam Malik ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne shighar se mana farmaya aur shighar ye hai ke aadmi apni beti ka nikah is shart par karey ke wo ( doosra ( bhi apni beti ka nikah us se karega aur un donon ke darmyan mehar na ho."
3466,"Ubaidullah ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ki tarah riwayat ki, albatta Ubaidullah ki hadis mein hai, unhon-ne kaha : maine Naafe se puchha : shighar kya hai?"
3467,"Abdur-Rehman siraaj ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne shighar se mana farmaya."
3468,ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke Nabi ‌(Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya shighar nahi hai Islam main .
3469,"ibne-Numair aur abu-Usama ne hamein Ubaidullah se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne abu-Zinad se, unhon-ne Aaraj se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne shighar se mana farmaya, ibne-Numair ne izafa kya : shighar ye hai ke aik aadmi doosrey se kahey : tum apni beti ka nikah mere sath kar do aur main apni beti ka nikah tumharey sath karta hun aur tum apni behan ka nikah mere sath kar do main apni behan ka nikah tumharey sath karta hun."
3470,"Abda ne Ubaidullah (bin umr ( se isi sanad ke sath ye ( hadis) bayan ki, aur unhon-ne ibne-Numair ka izafa zikr nahi kya."
3471,"ibne-Juraij ne hamein khabar di, kaha : mujhey abu-Zubair ne bataya ke unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, keh rahe they : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne shighaar se mana farmaya."
3472,"Yahya bin Ayub ne kaha : hamein Hushaim ne hadis bayan ki, ibne-Numair ne kaha : hamein Wakee ne hadis bayan ki, abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba ne kaha : hamein abu-Khalid Ahmar ne hadis sunai aur Muhammad-bin-Musanna ne kaha : hamein Yahya qattaan ne Abdul-Hameed bin Jafar se, unhon-ne Yazeed bin abi Habib se, unhon-ne Marsad bin-Abdullah Yazani se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aqba-bin-Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : sabse zyada poori kiye janey ke laaiq shart wo hai jis se tum ne sharmgahon ko halal kya hai. ye Abu-Bakar aur ibne- Musanna ki hadis ke alfaz hain, albatta ibne- Musanna ne ( الشرط ( ki bajaey) ( الشروط ( ) shartein wo hain) kaha hai."
3473,"Hisham ne Yahya-bin-abi-Kasir se hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein abu-Salma ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis bayan ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jis aurat ka khawind na raha ho iska nikah (us waqt tak) na kya jaey yahan tak ke us se poochh liya jaey aur kunwari ka nikah na kya jaey yahan tak ke us se ijazat li jaey. sahaba ne kaha : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! uski ijazat kaisey hogi ? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ( aisey (ke wo khamosh rahe ( inkar na kare. ("
3474,is sanad se bhi uper zikr ki gaee hadis isi tarah marvi hai
3475,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se us ladki ke barey mein puchha jiske ghar waley uska nikah ( karne ka irada ( karein, kya us se uski marzi malum ki jaeygi ya nahi ? to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya : haan , uski marzi malum ki jaeygi. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : maine aap se kaha : wo to yaqinan haya mehsus karegi , to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab wo khamosh rahi to yahi uski ijazat hogi"
3476,"Saeed bin Mansoor aur Qutaiba-bin-Saeed ne kaha : ham se Imam Malik ne hadis bayan ki. Yahya-bin-Yahya ne kaha : maine Imam Malik (Rehmatullahi-alaih) se puchha : kya aapko Abdullah-bin Fazal ne Naafe bin Juber ke waastey se Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se ye hadis bayan ki hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jis aurat ka shauhar na raha ho wo apne wali ki nisbat apne barey mein zyada haq rakhti hai, aur kunwari se uske (nikah ke) barey mein ijazat li jaey aur iska khamosh rehna uski ijazat hai? to Imam Malik ne jawab diya : haan."
3477,"Qutaiba-bin-Saeed ne kaha : hamein Sufiyan ne Ziyad bin Sad se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Abdullah-bin Fazal se riwayat ki, unhon-ne Naafe bin Juber ko Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se khabar detey huey suna ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jisne shadi shuda zindagi guzari ho wo apne barey mein apne wali ki nisbat zyada haq rakhti hai, aur kunwari se uski marzi poochhi jaey aur uski khamoshi uski ijazat hai."
3478,"ibne-abi-Umar ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Sufiyan ne isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki aur kaha : jis aurat ne shadi shuda zindagi guzari ho wo apne barey mein apne wali ki nisbat zyada haq rakhti hai, aur kunwari se uska walid uske (nikah ke) barey mein ijazat lega, uski khamoshi uski ijazat hai. aur kabhi unhon-ne kaha : aur uski khamoshi iska iqrar hai."
3479,"abu-Usama ne Hisham se, unhon-ne apne walid (Urwa) se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mere sath chh baras ki umr mein nikah kya aur jab main nau (9) baras ki thi to mere sath ghar basaya. kaha : ham ( hijrat ke baad) Madina aaey to main aik mahina bukhar mein mubtala rahi. (aur mere sar ke baal jhad gaey, jab sihatyaab hui to) phir mere baal (achi tarah se ug aaey yahan tak ke) gardan se nichey tak ki chutiya bin gaee. (un dinon aik roz meri walida) umme-Ruman (Raziallahu anhu) mere paas aaein jabke main jhooley par) jhol rahi ( thi aur mere sath meri saheliyan bhi thin, unhon-ne mujhey zor se awaz di, main unke paas gaee, mujhey malum na tha ke wo mujh se kya chahti hain. unhon-ne mera hath thama aur mujhey darwazey par la khada kya, (saans phoolney ki wjah se) mere munh se ha-ha ki awaz nikal rahi thi, yahan tak ke jab meri saans ( chadhney ki kaifiyat ( chali gaee to wo mujhey aik ghar ke andar ley aaein to ( ghair mutwaqqe taur par) wahan Ansar ki auratein (jama) thin, wo kehney lagin, khair w barkat par aur achchhey naseeb par (aai ho.) to unhon (meri walida) ne mujhey unke sipurd kar diya. unhon-ne mera sar dhoya, aur mujhey banaya sanwara, phir main iske siwa kisi baat par na chaunki ke achcha chasht ke waqt Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif ley aaey aur un aurton ne mujhey Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sipurd kar diya."
3480,"abu-Muawiya aur Abda bin Sulaiman ne Hisham se unhon-ne apne walid (Urwa) se unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mere sath nikah kya jab main chh saal ki thi aur mere sath ghar basaya jab main nau (9) saal ki thi."
3481,"Zohri ne Urwa se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse nikah kya jab wo saat (7) saal ki thin, aur ghar basaya jab wo nau (9) saal ki thin aur unke khiloney unke sath they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unhein chhod kar faut huey jab wo atthara saal ki thin."
3482,"Aswad ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse nikah kya jabke wo chh baras ki thin aur unki rukhsati hui jabke wo nau (9) baras ki thin aur aap faut huey jabke wo atthara baras ki thin."
3483,"Wakee ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Sufiyan ne Ismail bin Umayya se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Abdullah-bin Urwa se, unhon-ne Urwa se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Shawaal mein mere sath nikah kya, aur Shawaal hi mein mere sath ghar basaayaa , to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki beeviyon mein se kon si biwi aap ke yahan mujh se zyada khushnaseeb thi? (Urwa ne) kaha : Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) pasand karti thin ke apni (rishtedar aur zer kifaalat) aurton ki rukhsati Shawaal mein karein. (jabke Arbon mein purana tasawwur ye tha ke Shawaal mein nikah aur rukhsati shadi ke liye theek nahi.)"
3484,Abdullah-bin-Numair ne kaha : hamein Sufiyan ne isi sanad ke sath (ye) hadis bayan ki aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke amal (khandan ki bachchiyon ka Shawaal mein shadi karaaney) ka tazkira nahi kya.
3485,"Sufiyan ne hamein Yazeed bin Kaisan se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne abu-Hazim se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : main Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas hazir tha, aap ke paas aik aadmi aaya aur bataya ke usne Ansar ki aik aurat se nikah (tay) kya hai. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se farmaya : kya tum ne usey dekha hai? us ne jawab diya : nahi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jao aur usey dekh lo kyonke Ansar ki aankhon mein kuchh hai."
3486,"Marwan bin Muawiya Fazari ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Yazeed bin kaisan ne abu-Hazim se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein aik aadmi hazir hua aur kaha : maine Ansar ki aik aurat se nikah kya hai. Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se puchha : kya tum ne usey dekha hai? kyonke Ansar ki aankhon mein kuchh hai. us ne jawab diya : maine usey dekha hai. aap ne puchha : kitney mehar par tum ne us se nikah kya hai? us ne jawab diya : char auqiya par. to Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se farmaya : char auqiya chandi par? maano tum us pahad ke pahlu se chandi tarashtey ho! tumhen dene ke liye hamarey paas kuchh maujood nahi, albatta jald hi ham tumhen aik lashkar mein bhej dengey tumhen us se ( ghaneemat ka hissa) mil jaeyga kaha : iske baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne banu-abas ki taraf aik lashkar rawana kya (to (us aadmi ko bhi usmein bhej diya."
3487,"Yaqoob bin Abdur-Rehman al-Qari aur Abdul-Azeez bin abi Hazim ne abu-Hazim se, unhon-ne Hazrat Sahal-bin-Sad Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : aik khatun Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hui, aur kaha : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam)! main apni zaat aapko hiba karne ke liye hazir hui hon, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne uski taraf nazar ki, aap apni nazar nichey se uper aur uper se nichey tak ley gaey. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apna sar Mubarak jhuka liya. jab aurat ne dekha ke aap ne iske barey mein koi faisla nahi kya to wo baith gaee. is par aap ke sahaba mein se aik aadmi khada hua aur kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! agar aapko us (ke sath shadi) ki zarurat nahi to uski shadi mere sath kar dein. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha : kya tumharey paas (mehar mein dene ke liye) koi cheez hai? us ne jawab diya : Allah ki qasam! Allah ke rasool! (kuchh) nahi hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : apne ghar walon ke paas jao, dekho tumhen kuchh milta hai? wo gaya phir wapas aaya aur kaha : nahi, Allah ki qasam! mujhey kuchh nahi mila. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : dekho ! chahey lohey ki anguthi ho. wo gaya phir wapas aaya, aur arz ki, nahi, Allah ki qasam! Allah ke rasool! lohey ki anguthi bhi nahi hai, albatta meri ye tehband hai. Sehal ne kaha : uske paas (kandhey ki) chadar bhi nahi thi. usmein se aadhi ( bataur mehar ( uske liye hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : wo tumharey tehband ka kya karegi, agar tum usey pahnogey to us (ke jism) par usmein se kuchh nahi hoga aur agar wo pahnegi to tum par usmein se kuchh nahi hoga. is par wo aadmi baith gaya. usey baithey huey lamba waqt ho gaya to wo khada ho gaya (aur chal diya.) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey peeth pher kar jatey huey dekh liya. aap ne uske barey mein hukm diya to usey Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khaatir bula liya gaya, jab wo aaya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tumharey paas Quran kitna hai? ( tumhen kitna Quran yad hai? ( usne kaha : mere paas falan sura aur falan sura hai. us ne wo soortein ginin. to aap ne puchha : tum unhein zabani padhtey ho? us ne arz ki, ji haan! Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jao, tumhen jitna Quran yad hai iske iwaz (nikah ke liye) tumhen iska Malik (khaawind) bana diya gaya hai. ye ibne-abu-Hazim ki hadis hai, Yaqoob ki hadis bhi alfaz mein usi ke qareeb hai."
3488,"Hammad-bin-Zaid , Sufiyan-bin-Uena, darawardi aur Zayda sab ne abu-Hazim se, unhon-ne Sahal-bin-Sad (Raziallahu anhu) se yahi hadis bayan ki, unmein se kuchh rawi dusron par izafa kartey hain. magar Zayda ki hadis mein hai ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jao, maine us se tumhari shadi kar di hai, isliye ( ab ( tum usey Quran ki taleem do."
3489,"abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ahliya, (Ummul-Momenin) Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se puchha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (ki beeviyon) ka mehar kitna (hota ( tha? unhon-ne jawab diya : apni beeviyon ke liye aap ka mehar baara auqiya aur aik nash tha. ( phir ( unhon-ne puchha : jantey ho nash kya hai? maine kaha : nahi, unhon-ne kaha : aadha auqiya, ye kul 500 dirham bantey hain aur yahi apni beeviyon ke liye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka mehar tha."
3490,"Sabit ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Hazrat Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf (Raziallahu anhu) (ke libaas) par zard (zafran ki khushbu ka ( nishan dekha to farmaya : ye kya hai? unhon-ne jawab diya : Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! maine soney ki aik guthli ke wazan par aik aurat se shadi ki hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah tumhen barkat de. walima karo, chahe aik bakri se karo."
3491,"abu-Awana ne hamein Qatada se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ahade-mubaarak mein Hazrat Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf (Raziallahu anhu) ne soney ki guthli ke wazan ke barabar soney ke iwaz nikah kya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya : walima karo chahe aik bakri se karo."
3492,"Wakee ne hamein khabar di, kaha : hamein Shoba ne Qatada aur humaid se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Hazrat Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf (Raziallahu anhu) ne soney ki aik guthli ke wazan ke barabar soney ke iwaz nikah kya aur ye ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya : walima karo chahe aik bakri se karo."
3493,"Abu-Dawud , Wahab bin Jarir aur Shababaa sab ne Shoba se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Humaid se isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki, albatta Wahab ki hadis mein yun hai : unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : maine aik aurat se shadi ki hai."
3494,"Ishaq-bin-Ibrahim aur Muhammad-bin Qudama ne kaha : hamein Nazar-bin-Shumail ne khabar di, kaha : hamein Shoba ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Abdul-Azeez bin Suheb ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : maine Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se suna wo keh rahe they : Hazrat Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey dekha jabke mujh par shadi ki bashaashat (khushi) numayan thi, maine kaha : maine Ansar ki aik aurat se shadi ki hai, aap ne puchha : tum ne usey kitna mehar diya hai? maine kaha : aik guthli aur Ishaq ki hadis mein hai : soney ki."
3495,"Abu-Dawod ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Shoba ne abu-Hamza se hadis bayan ki. Shoba ne kaha : unka naam Abdur-Rehman bin abi Abdullah ( kaisaan ( hai. unhon-ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Hazrat Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf (Raziallahu anhu) ne soney ki guthli ke wazan ke barabar ( soney (ke iwaz aik aurat se shadi ki."
3496,"Wahab ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne isi sanad ke sath ye hadis bayan ki, magar unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf (Raziallahu anhu) ke beton mein se aik ne kaha : soney ki (eik guthli.)"
3497,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jihad kya khaibar par aur ham logon ne wahan Namaz padhi subah ke bahut andherey main aur sawar huey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur sawar huey abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) aur main radeef tha abu-Talha ka, aur rawaana huey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) galiyon mein khaibar ki aur mera zaanu Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke raan se lag lag jata tha aur tehband Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki aap ki raan se khisak gaee thi aur main dekhta safedi aap ki raan ki, phir jab Shahar ke andar gaey aap ne farmaya Allahu-akbar kharaab hua khaibar ham jab utartey hain kisi qaum ke aangan main to bura hota hai haal daraiye gaey logon ka. un kalimat ko aap ne teen baar padha yani انا اذا نزلنا b-saakhta qaum se akheer tak aur itney mein wahan ke log apne apney kaamon mein nikley aur unhon-ne kaha ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aa chukey aur Abdul-Azeez ne kaha ke hamarey logon ne ye bhi kaha ke lashkar bhi aa gaya. kaha rawi ne ke gharaz ham ne ley liya khaibar ko jabran aur qaidi log jama kiye gaey aur Dahiya aaey aur kaha ke ya Rasulullah ! aik londi mujhey inayat kijiye un qaidiyon mein se. aap ne farmaya ke jao aik londi ley lo. unhon-ne Safiya-binte-Huyi ko ley liya aur aik shakhs ne aa ke kaha ke aey Nabi Allah Taala ke aap ne Dahiya ko Huyi ki beti de-di jo sardar hai bani-Quraiza aur bani Nazir ka aur wo kisi ke laaiq nahi siwa aap ke to farmaya ke bulao unko us londi ke sath. kaha rawi ne ke phir wo usey lekar aaey phir jab aap ne usko dekha to Dahiya se farmaya ke tum koi aur londi ley lo qaidiyon mein se iske siwa . kaha rawi ne ke phir aap ne aazad kya Safiya (Raziallahu anhu) ko aur unse nikah kar liya so Sabit ne unse kaha ke aey abu-Hamza ! unka mehar kya baandha unhon-ne ? kaha yahi mehar tha ke unko aazad kar diya aur nikah kar liya yahan tak ke phir jab wo raah mein they, to singar kar diya unka Umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu) ne aur pesh kar diya aap par unko raat mein aur subah ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) nosha baney huey they. phir farmaya aap ne jiske paas jo kuchh ho (yani khaney ki qism se) wo laey aur aik dastar-khuwan chamdey ka bichha diya aur koi paneer laney laga aur koi khajoor aur koi ghi un sab ko tod-taad kar khub milaya aur ye walima hua Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka."
3498,"Hammad, yani ibne-zaid ne Sabit aur Abdul-Azeez bin Suheb se, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se. Hammad ne Sabit aur Shuaib bin (hab-haab) se, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se. isi tarah abu-Awana ne Qatada aur Abdul-Azeez se, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se. abu-Awana (hi) ne abu-Usman se, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se. Muaz bin Hisham ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Shuaib bin Habhab se, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se aur isi tarah Yonus-bin-ubaid ne Shuaib bin ( Habhab) se, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se aur un sab ne (kaha : unhon-ne) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne Hazrat Safiya (Raziallahu anhu) ko aazad kya aur unki aazadi ko unka mehar muqarrar kya. Muaz ki apne walid ( Hisham ( se riwayat ki hui hadis mein hai : Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Safiya (Raziallahu anhu) se nikah farmaya aur unki aazadi, unko mehar mein di."
3499,"Hazrat abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us shakhs ke barey mein, jo apni londi ko aazad karta hai, phir us se shadi karta hai, farmaya : uske liye 2 ajr hain. ( aazad karne ka ajr aur uske baad shadi ke zariey usey izzat ka maqam dene ka ajr.)"
3500,"saiyedna Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : main radeef tha saiyedna abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ka khaibar ke din aur qadam mera chhu jata tha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke qadam se, phir pahunchey ham khaibar walon ke paas jab suraj nikla aur un logon ne apne chaupayon ko nikala tha aur wo apne kudal aur tokri aur phaawdey lekar nikley aur kehney lagey : Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur khamis yani donon aa gaey. kaha rawi ne ke farmaya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne '' kharaab hua khaibar aur jab ham utartey hain kisi qaum ke aangan mein (so bura anjam hota hai daraaey gaey logon ka.)'' (Saffat : 177) aur Allah Taala ne unko shikast di aur Dahiya (Raziallahu anhu) ke hisse mein aik baandi khoobsurat aai aur khareed liya usko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne saat (7) shakhson ke badley mein aur phir sipurd kya usko Umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu) ke ke singaar kar dein unka aur taiyaar kar dein unko Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye aur kaha rawi ne ke guman karta hun main ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne isliye unke sipurd kya ke wo unke ghar mein iddat poori karey, yani aik haiz ke sath istibra unka ho jo hukm hai baandi ka aur ye Sayeda Safiya (Raziallahu anhu) beti thin Huyi ki aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unka walima kya khajoor aur Aqit se aur ghi se aur zamin mein kai garhey khodey gaey aur is mein dastar-khuwaan chamdey ka bichhaa diya gaya, garhey isliye khodey ke ghi idhar-udhar na janey paaey aur aqit aur ghi laey aur is mein daal diya aur logon ne khub sair ho kar khaya aur log kehney lagey ke ham nahi jantey ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse nikah kya ya unko Umme- walad banaya phir logon ne kaha ke agar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unko chhipaya to jano ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki biwi hain aur agar na chhipaya to jano ke umme-walad hain, phir jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sawar honey lagey to un par parda kya aur wo oont ke sireen par baithin, so logon ne jaan liya ke unse nikah kya hai phir jab Madina ke qareeb pahunch gaey jaldi chalaaya oonton ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aur jaldi chalaaya ham ne aur thokar khaai azba ontni ne ye naam hai Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ontni ka aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) girey aur Sayeda Safiya (Raziallahu anhu) bhi girin so Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) uthey aur un par parda kar liya aur auratein dekhney lagin aur kehney lagin Allah door karey yahoodiya ko . kaha rawi ne maine kaha aey Hamza, kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) gir padey? to unhon-ne kaha : haan Allah ki qism ! Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) gir padey aur saiyedna Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke main Sayeda Zenab Ummul-Momenin (Raziallahu anhu) ke walima mein bhi hazir tha aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne logon ko aasuda aur sair kar diya roti aur gosht se aur mujhey Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bhejtey they ke logon ko bula laaun phir jab khilaaney se farigh ho chukey. khadey huey aur main Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke peechhey hua 2 log Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hujrey mein reh gaey (yani jahan Zenab (Raziallahu anha) thin) aur unko baton ne bitha rakha aur wo na nikley so Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni beebiyon ke hujron par jatey they aur har aik par salam kartey they aur farmatey they : ke ''kaisey ho tum aey ghar waalo! ''wo kehti thin ke ham khairiyat se hain, aey Allah ke rasool! aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni bi-bi ko kaisa paya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farmatey : ke '' khair se hain.'' phir jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sab ki khair w aafiyat poochhney se farigh huey lautey aur main bhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath lota aur jab darwazey par pahunchey to dekha ke wo donon shakhs maujood hain aur baton mein mashghool hain. phir jab un donon ne dekha ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) lautey, khadey ho gaey aur bahar nikley so Allah ki qism hai ke mujhey yad nahi raha ke maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko khabar di ya Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par wahi utri ke wo donon shakhs chaley gaey aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) lot kar aaey yani hujra Zenab (Raziallahu anha) par aur main bhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath aaya. phir jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne pair rakha darwazey ki chaukhat par, parda daal diya mere aur apne beech mein aur ye aayat Mubarak utri ( لاَ تَدْخُلُوا بُيُوتَ النَّبِىِّ إِلاَّ أَنْ يُؤْذَنَ لَكُمْ) ''na dakhil ho tum Nabi ke ghar mein magar jab unki taraf se ijazat ho tum ko.''"
3501,"Sulaiman-bin Mughira ne hamein Sabit se hadis bayan ki kaha : Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne hamein hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat Safiya Hazrat Dahiya (Raziallahu anhu) ke hissey mein aa gain , (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Dahiya (Raziallahu anhu) ko apne hissey ki aik kaneez leney ki ijazat de kar ghair rasmi taur par taqseem ki shuruat kar di thi.) log Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas unki tareef karne lagey, wo keh rahe they : ham ne qaidiyon mein un jaisi aurat nahi dekhi. to aap ne Dahiya (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf paigham bheja, aur unke badley mein jo unhon-ne chaha, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne diya, phir aap ne usey meri walida ke sipurd kya aur farmaya : usey bana sanwaar do. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khaibar se nikley, yahan tak ke jab aap ne usey pusht ki taraf kar liya, (khaibar peechhey reh gaya) to aap ne padao daala, phir un (hazrat Safiya (Raziallahu anhu)) ke liye khema lagwaaya, jab subah hui to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jiske paas zaade- raah se zayed kuchh ho wo usey hamarey paas ley aaey. kaha : is par koi aadmi zayed khajoorein lekar aaney laga aur (koii) zayed sattu, yahan tak ke logon ne un chizon se aik dher makhloot khaney (Hais) ka bana liya, phir wo us hais mein se tanaawul karne lagey aur barish ke pani ke hauzon se jo unke qareeb they pani peeney lagey. kaha : Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ye tha un (Safiya (Raziallahu anhu)) ke liye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka walima. kaha : iske baad ham chal padey, jab ham ne Madina ki diwarein dekhin to ham shiddate-shauq se uski taraf lapak padey, ham ne apni sawaariyan utha dein (tez kar din) aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bhi apni sawari utha di. kaha : Safiya (Raziallahu anhu) aap ke peechhey thin, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein apne sath sawar kar liya tha. kaha : (achanak) Rasulullah ki sawari ko thokar lagi to aap zamin par aa rahe aur wo (Hazrat Safiya (Raziallahu anhu)) bhi zamin par aa rahin, kaha : logon mein se koi bhi na Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf dekh raha tha aur na unki taraf, kaha : yahan tak ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khadey huey aur Hazrat Safiya (Raziallahu anhu) ke aagey parda kya, phir ham aap ki khidmat mein hazir huey, to aap ne farmaya : hamein koi nuqsan nahi pahuncha . phir ham Madina ke andar dakhil huey to aap ki beeviyon ki baandiyan bahar nikal aain, wo aik dusri ko wo (Safiya (Raziallahu anhu)) dikha rahi thin, aur unke girney par dil hi dil mein khush ho rahi thin."
3502,"Muhammad-bin-Hatim bin Memun ne mujhey hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Behaz ne hadis sunai, neez Muhammad-bin Raafe ne mujhey hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein abu-Nazar Hashim bin-Qasim ne hadis sunai, un donon (Bahaz aur abu-Nazar) ne kaha : hamein Sulaiman-bin Mughira ne Sabit se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki. ye Behaz ki hadis hai. kaha : jab Hazrat Zenab (Raziallahu anha) ki iddat guzri to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Hazrat Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya : in ( Zenab (Raziallahu anha) (ke samney unki mere sath shadi ka zikr karo. kaha : to Hazrat Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) chaley yahan tak ke unke paas pahunchey to wo apne aatey mein Khameer mila rahi thin, kaha : jab maine unko dekha to mere dil mein unki azmat baith gaee yahan tak ke main unki taraf nazar bhi na utha sakta tha kyonke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne un (ke sath shadi) ka zikr kya tha, maine unki taraf apni peeth ki aur eidiyon ke bal muda aur kaha : Zenab ! Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne tumhara zikr kartey huey paigham bheja hai. unhon-ne kaha : main kuchh karne wali nahi yahan tak ke apne rab se mashwara (istikhaara) kar loon, aur wo uth kar apni Namaz ki jagah ki taraf chali gain aur) idhar ( Quran nazil ho gaya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) baghair ijazat liye unke paas tashrif ley aaey. ( Sulaiman-bin Mughira ne) kaha : ( Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : maine apne aap samet sab logon ko dekha ke jab din ka ujala phail gaya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein roti aur gosht khilaaya. iske baad) aksar ( log nikal gaey, chand baqi reh gaey. wo khaney ke baad (aap ke) ghar main hi baatein karne lagey. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (wahan se) nikley, main bhi aap ke peechhey ho liya, aap yakey baad doosrey apni beeviyon ke hujron ki taraf ja kar unhein salam kehney lagey. wo (jawab de kar) kehtin : Allah ke rasool! Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni ( nai ( ahliya ko kaisa paya ? ( Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : main nahi janta maine aapko bataya ke log ja chukey hain ya aap ne mujhey bataya . phir aap chal padey yahan tak ke ghar mein dakhil ho gaey. main bhi aap ke sath dakhil honey laga to aap ne mere aur apne darmyan parda latka diya aur (is waqt) hijaab (ka hukm) nazil hua, kaha : aur logon ko (is munaasibat se) jo nasihat ki jaani thi kar di gaee. ibne-Raafe ne apni hadis mein ye izafa kya : aey eman waalo! tum Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke gharon mein dakhil na hua karo magar ye ke tumhen khaney ke liye ( aaney ki) ijazat di jaey, us haal main ( aao (ke iske pakney ka intizar na kar rahe ho ( khaney ke waqt aao pahley na aao ( se lekar us farman tak : aur Allah haq se sharm nahi karta."
3503,"abu-Rabee Zahrani, abu-Kamil Fuzel bin Husain aur Qutaiba-bin-Saeed ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Hammad ne, wo (jo ( Zaid ke betey hain, Sabit se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki. abu-Kamil ki riwayat mein hai : maine Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se suna. unhon-ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko nahi dekha ke aap ne kisi biwi kaa. abu-Kaamil ne kaha : apni beeviyon mein se kisi biwi ki kisi cheez ( khushi ( par. us jaisa walima kya ho jaisa Hazrat Zenab (Raziallahu anha) (ke sath nikah ( par kya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (is mauqe par) bakri zabah ki."
3504,"Abdul-Azeez bin Suheb se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se suna wo keh rahe they : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni beeviyon mein se kisi biwi ka us se badh kar ya us se behtar walima nahi kya jaisa walima Hazrat Zenab (Raziallahu anha) ka kya. Sabit Bunani ne puchha : aap ne kis cheez se walima kya tha? unhon-ne jawab diya : aap ne unhein roti aur gosht khilaaya yahan tak ke unhon-ne (sair ho kar khana) chhod diya."
3505,"Yahya bin Habib haarisi, Aasim bin nazar Taimi aur Muhammad-bin Abdul-Aala ne hamein hadis bayan ki, sab ne Motamir se riwayat ki. lafz ( Yahya (bin Habib ke hain. kaha : ham se Motamir bin Sulaiman ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine apne walid se suna, unhon-ne kaha : hamein abu-Mujliz ne saiyedna Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Zenab binte- (Jahas) (Raziallahu anhu) se nikah kya to aap ne logon ko (khaney ki) dawat di, unhon-ne khana khaya, phir baith kar baatein karne lagey. kaha : aap ne aisa andaz ikhtiyar farmaya maano ke khadey honey lagey hon is par bhi wo na uthey, jab aap ne ye surate-haal dekhi to aap khadey ho gaey, jab aap khadey huey to logon mein se bhi jo khadey huey, wo ho gaey. Aasim aur ibne- Abdul-Aala ne apni hadis mein izafa kya : kaha teen aadmi baithey rahe, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (hujrey mein) dakhil honey ke liye tashrif ley aaey, to (us waqt bhi) wo log baithey huey they, phir (kuchh der baad) wo uthey aur chaley gaey. (Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : maine aa kar Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko khabar di ke wo ja chukey hain. aap tashrif laey aur andar dakhil huey, mein bhi dakhil honey laga to aap ne mere aur apne darmyan parda latka diya. kaha : aur (is mauqe par) izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ne (ye aayat ( nazil farmai : aey eman waalo! tum Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke gharon mein dakhil na hua karo, siwaey-iske ke tumhen khaney ke liye ijazat di jaey, aisey (waqt mein) aao ke (aa kar) iske pakney ka intizar karne waley na ho ( khana rakh diya jaey to aao) us farman tak : bila shubah ye baat Allah ke nazdeek bahut badi thi."
3506,"ibne-Shahab ne kaha : Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : pardey (ke ehkaam ( ko sab logon se zyada jaanney wala mein hun. Hazrat Ubai-bin-Kab (Raziallahu anhu) bhi iske barey mein mujh se puchha kartey they. Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Hazrat Zenab binte- Jahash (Raziallahu anhu) ke dulhaa ki haisiyat se subah ki, aap ne (usi raat ( Madina mein unse shadi ki thi, din chadhney ke baad aap ne logon ko khaney ke liye bulaya , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif farma huey to kuchh afraad logon ke chaley janey ke baad bhi aap ke sath baithey rahe, yahan tak ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khadey ho gaey. aap chaley to main bhi aap ke sath chal padaa yahan tak ke aap (sab hujron se hotey huey) hujrae-Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke darwazey par pahunchey. phir aap ne socha ke wo log ja chukey hongey, aap wapas huey, main bhi aap ke sath wapas aaya, to tab bhi wo apni jaghon par baithey huey they. aap lot gaey aur main bhi dobara lot gaya, yahan tak ke aap Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke hujrey tak pahunchey to phir se wapas aaey, main bhi aap ke sath wapas aaya, to dekha ke wo log uth ( kar ja) chukey they, iske baad aap ne mere aur apne darmyan parda latka diya, aur (us waqt) pardey ki aayat nazil ki gaee."
3507,"Jafar bin Sulaiman ne hamein abu-Usman Jaad se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne shadi ki aur apni ahliya ke paas tashrif ley gaey. meri walida umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu) ne hais taiyaar kya, usey aik piyala numa badey bartan mein daala , aur kaha : Anas ! ye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein le jao aur arz karo : ye meri walida ne aap ki khidmat mein bheja hai, aur wo aapko salam arz karti hain aur kehti hain : Allah ke rasool! ye hamari taraf se aap ke liye thodi si cheez hai. kaha : main usey lekar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur kaha : meri walida aapko salam pesh karti hain aur kehti hain : Allah ke rasool! ye aap ke liye hamari taraf se thodi si cheez hai. aap ne farmaya : usey rakh do (aap ne usey bhi waleemey ke khaney ke sath shamil kar liya ( phir farmaya : Mina jao, falan-falan aur falan aur jo log tumhen milein unhein bula laao. aap ne chand aadmiyon ke naam liye. kaha : main un logon ko jinke aap ne naam liye aur wo jo mujhey miley, unko ley aaya. kaha : maine Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha : wo (sab) tadaad mein kitney they? unhon-ne jawab diya : teen so ke lagbhag. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se farmaya : Anas ! bartan ley aao. kaha : log andar dakhil huey yahan tak ke suffa ( chabootra (aur hujra bhar gaya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : das das afraad halqa bana lein, aur har insan apne samney se khaey. un sab ne khaya yahan tak ke sair ho gaey, aik giroh nikla to doosra dakhil hua (is tarah hota raha ( yahan tak ke un sab ne khana kha liya, to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey hukm diya : Anas! utha lo. to maine (bartan) utha liye, mujhey malum nahi ke jab maine ( khana ( rakha tha us waqt zyada tha ya jab maine uthaya us waqt. kaha : unmein se kuchh toliyan Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ghar main hi baith kar baatein karne lagin, jabke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) baithey huey they, aur aap ki ahliya diwar ki taraf rukh kiye baithi thin, ye log Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par nagawar guzarney lagey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ( ghar se) nikley, (ek ke baad ek) apni beeviyon ko salam kya, phir wapas huey. jab unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha ke aap wapas ho gaey hain, to unhon-ne mehsus kya ke wo aap par nagawar guzar rahe hain. kaha : to wo jaldi se darwazey ki taraf lapkey aur sab ke sab nikal gaey, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ( aagey ( tashrif laaey, yahan tak ke aap ne parda latkaya aur andar dakhil ho gaey aur main hujra (numa chabootrey) mein betha hua tha, aap thodi hi der thahrey, yahan tak ke) dobara) bahar mere paas aaey, aur (aap par) ye aayat nazil ki gaee. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bahar tashrif laey aur logon ke samney unhein (aayate-kareema ke jumla kalimaat ko) tilawat farmaya : aey eman waalo! tum Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke gharon mein dakhil na hua karo siwaey-iske ke tumhen khaney ke liye ijazat di jaey, khana pakney ka intizar kartey huey nahi, balke jab tumhen dawat di jaey tab tum andar jao, phir jab khana kha chuko to muntashir ho jao, aur) wahin ( baton mein dil lagaatey huey nahi (baithey raho.) bila shubah ye baat Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko takleef deti hai aayat ke aakhir tak. Jaad ne kaha : Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : un aayaton ke sath (jo aik hi lambi aayat mein samo di gain) mera talluq sabse zyada qareeb ka hai, aur (unke nuzool hotey hi) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki beeviyon (Raziallahu anha) ko parda kara diya gaya."
3508,"Mamar ne hamein abu-Usman (Jaad) se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Hazrat Zenab (Raziallahu anha) se nikah kya to Umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu) ne aik badey bartan mein hais bhi aap ki khidmat mein bataur hadiya pesh kya. Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jao aur musalmanon mein se jo bhi tumhen miley usey mere paas bula lao to main jis se mila usey aap ki taraf dawat di, log aap ki khidmat mein hazir hotey, khana khaatey aur nikal jatey. Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khaney par apna hath rakha aur us mein) barkat ki) dua ki, uske barey mein jo Allah ne chaha ke aap kahein, aap ne kaha, aur main jisko bhi mila, unmein se kisi aik ko bhi nahi chhoda magar usey dawat di, logon ne khaya, yahan tak ke sair ho gaey aur nikal gaey, unmein se aik giroh ( wahin) reh gaya, unhon-ne aap ki maujudgi mein lambi guftgu ki, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) haya mehsus karne lagey ke unse kuchh kahein, chunanche aap nikley aur unhein ghar main hi chhod diya, to Allah Taala ne (ye aayatein ( nazil farmaein : aey eman waalo! tum Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke gharon mein dakhil na hua karo, siwaey-iske ke tumhen khaney ke liye (andar aaney ki) ijazat di jaey, khana pakney ka intizar kartey huey nahi. Qatada ne kaha : khaney ke waqt ka intizar kartey huey nahi. lekin jab tumhen bulaya jaey tab tum andar jao . yahan tak ke aap ne yahan tak tilawat ki : ye tumharey aur unke dilon ke liye aur zyada pakeezgi (ka tariqa ( hai."
3509,"Imam Malik ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tum mein se kisi ko waleemey ki dawat di jaey to wo usmein zaroor aaey."
3510,"Khalid-bin Haris ne hamein Ubaidullah (bin Umar-bin Hafs madni) se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tum mein se kisi ko waleemey ki dawat di jaey to wo qabool kare. Khalid ne kaha : Ubaidullah usey shadi (ki dawate-walima) par mahmool kartey they."
3511,"Muhammad-bin-Abdullah bin Numer ke walid ne kaha : hamein Ubaidullah ne Naafe se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tum mein se kisi ko shadi ke waleemey ki dawat di jaey to wo qabool kare."
3512,"Hammad ne hamein Ayub se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tumhen bulaya jaey to dawat mein aao ."
3513,"Mamar ne hamein Ayub se khabar di, unhon-ne Naafe se riwayat ki ke Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se (hadis bayan kartey huey) kaha kartey they : jab tum mein se koi apne bhai ko dawat de to wo qabool karey shadi ho ya us jaisi (koi aur) taqreeb."
3514,"Zubaidi ne hamein Naafe se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jis shakhs ko shadi ya us jaisi kisi taqreeb mein bulaya jaey to wo qabool kare."
3515,"Ismail bin umaiyya ne hamein Naafe se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tumhen bulaya jaey to dawat mein aao."
3516,"Musa-bin-Aqba ne Naafe se khabar di, unhon-ne kaha : maine Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : (musalman bhaiyon ki taraf se di janey wali) us dawat ko, jab tumhen uske liye bulaya jaey, qabool karo. kaha : Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) dawat mein Sharik hotey chahe wo shadi ki ho ya shadi ke baghair, aur wo rozey ki haalat mein bhi usmein aatey they."
3517,"Umar-bin Muhammad ne mujhey Naafe se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tumhen ( bakri ke) paaey ki bhi dawat di jaey to qabool karo."
3518,"Muhammad-bin-Musanna ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Abdur-Rehman-bin-Mehdi ne hadis sunai, neez hamein Muhammad-bin-Abdullah bin Numer ne hadis sunai, unhon-ne kaha : hamein mere walid ne hadis bayan ki, donon (ibne-Mehdi aur Abdullah-bin-Numair) ne kaha : hamein Sufiyan aur abu-Zubair se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tum mein se kisi ko khaney ki dawat di jaey to wo usmein aaey, phir agar aur chahey to kha ley, chahey to na khaaey. ibne-Musanna ne khaney ki dawat ke alfaz zikr nahi kiye."
3519,ibne-Juraij ne abu-Zubair se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki.
3520,"Ibne-Sirin ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tum mein se kisi ko dawat di jaey to wo qabool kare. agar wo roze-daar hai to dua karey aur agar rozey ke baghair hai to khana khaaey ."
3521,"Imam Malik ne ibne-Shahab se, unhon-ne Aaraj se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, wo kaha kartey they is walimey ka khana bura khana hai jis mein ameeron ko bulaya jaey aur miskinon ko chhod diya jaey aur jisne ( bulaney ke bawajud ( dawat mein shirkat na ki, us ne Allah aur uske rasool ki nafarmani ki."
3522,"Sufiyan (bin Uena ( ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : maine imam Zohri se puchha : janab Abu-Bakar ! ye hadis kis tarah hai : badtareen khana ameeron ka khana hai? wo hansey , aur jawab diya : ye ( hadis) is tarah nahi hai ke badtareen khana ameeron ka khana hai. Sufiyan ne kaha : mere walid ghani they, jab maine ye hadis suni thi to usne mujhey ghabraahat mein daal diya, isliye maine iske barey mein imam Zohri se malum kya, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Abdur-Rehman Aaraj ne hadis bayan ki ke unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they : badtareen khana us walimey ka khana hai. aagey Imam Malik (Rehmatullahi-alaih) ki hadis ki tarah bayan kya."
3523,"Mamar ne Zohri se khabar di, unhon-ne Saeed-bin-Musaiyab se aur Aaraj se, aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : badtareen khana us walimey ka khana hai, (aagey) Imam Malik (Rehmatullahi-alaih) ki hadis ki tarah hai"
3524,"abu-Zinad ne Aaraj se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se usi ki tarah hadis riwayat ki."
3525,"Ziyad bin Sad ne kaha : maine Sabit (bin ayaaz) Aaraj se suna, wo Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan kar rahe they ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : badtareen khana (aisey) walimey ka khana hai ke jo usmein aata hai usey us se roka jata hai aur jo us (mein shumooliyat ( se inkar karta hai usey bulaya jata hai. aur jis shakhs ne dawat qabool na ki, us ne Allah aur uske rasool ki nafarmani ki."
3526,"Sufiyan ne hamein Zohri se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Urwa se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rifaa (bin Samual Qarzi) ki biwi (Tameema binte-Wahab Qarziya) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hui aur kaha : main Rifaa ke yahan (nikah mein) thi, usne mujhey talaaq di aur qatae (teesri) talaaq de di to maine Abdur-Rehman bin Zuber se shadi kar li, magar jo uske paas hai wo kapdey ki jhaalar ki tarah hai. is par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) muskuraaey aur farmaya : kya tum dobara Rifaa ke paas lautna chahti ho? nahi (ja sakti), yahan tak ke tum us (doosrey khawind) ki lazzat chakh lo aur wo tumhari lazzat chakh ley. (hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne) kaha : Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) aap ke paas maujood they aur Khalid (Raziallahu anhu) (bin Saeed bin aas) darwazey par ijazat milney ke muntazir they, to unhon-ne pukar kar kaha : Abu-Bakar! kya aap us aurat ko nahi sun rahe jo baat wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas unchi awaz se keh rahi hai?"
3527,"Yunus ne ibne-Shahab se khabar di, kaha : mujhey Urwa-bin-Zubair ne hadis bayan ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki bevi mohtarma Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne unhein khabar di ke Rifaa Qarzi ne apni biwi ko talaaq de di aur qatae (aakhiri) talaaq de di, to us aurat ne iske baad Abdur-Rehman bin Zuber ( Qarzi ( se shadi kar li, baad azan wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aai , aur kehney lagi : aey Allah ke rasool! wo Rifaa ke nikah mein thi, us ne usey teen talaaq bhi de di, to maine iske baad Abdur-Rehman bin Zuber se shadi kar li aur wo , Allah ki qism ! uske paas to kapdey ke kinarey ki jhaalar ki manind (tarah) hi hai, aur us ne apni chadar ke kinarey ki jhaalar pakad li. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) muskuraaey aur farmaya : shayad tum Rifaa ke paas jana chahti ho? nahi! yahan tak ke wo tumhari lazzat chakh ley aur tum uski lazzat chakh lo. Hazrat Abu-Bakar siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas baithey they aur Khalid-bin Saeed bin Aas (Raziallahu anhu) hujrey ke darwazey par baithey huey they, unhein ( abhi andar aaney ki) ijazat nahi mili thi. kaha : to Khalid ne ( wahin se) Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ko pukaarna shuru kar diya : aap us aurat ko sakhti se is baat se roktey kyon nahi jo wo buland awaz se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas keh rahi hai."
3528,"Mamar ne hamein Zohri se khabar di, unhon-ne Urwa se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke Rifaa Qarzi ne apni biwi ko talaaq de di to Abdur-Rehman bin Zuber ne us aurat se nikah kar liya. wo Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hui aur kehney lagi : Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! Rifaa ne usey teen talaaqon mein se aakhiri talaaq bhi de di hai. jis tarah Yunus ki hadis hai."
3529,"abu-Usama ne hamein Hisham se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne apne walid (Urwa-bin-Zubair) se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se us aurat ke barey mein sawal kya gaya jis se koi aadmi nikah karey, phir wo usey talaaq de dey, iske baad wo kisi aur aadmi se nikah kar ley aur wo iske sath mubashrat karne se pahley usey talaaq de dey to kya wo aurat apne pahley shauhar ke liye halal (ho jati) hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : nahi, yahan tak ke wo ( doosra khawind) uski lazzat chakh ley."
3530,ibne-Fuzail aur abu-Muawia ne Hisham se isi sanad ke sath (yahi) hadis bayan ki.
3531,"Ali-bin-Mus-hir ne Ubaidullah-bin-Umar (bin Hafs umri) se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Qasim-bin-Muhammad se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : aik aadmi ne apni biwi ko teen talaaqein dein, iske baad aik aur aadmi ne us se nikah kya, phir us ne iske sath mubashrat karne se pahley us aurat ko talaaq de di to iske pahley shauhar ne chaha ke us se nikah kar ley. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se us masley ke barey mein puchha gaya to aap ne farmaya : nahi, yahan tak ke doosra (khaawind) uski (wahi) lazzat chakh ley jo pahley ne chakhi."
3532,"Abdullah-bin-Numair aur Yahya-bin-Saeed ne Ubaidullah se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah riwayat ki, aur Ubaidullah se riwayat ki hui Yahya ki hadis mein hai : hamein Qasim ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se hadis bayan ki."
3533,"saiyedna Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar koi tum mein se hambistari ke waqt ( ‏‏‏‏بِاسْمِ اللَّهِ اللَّهُمَّ جَنِّبْنَا الشَّيْطَانَ وَجَنِّبِ الشَّيْطَانَ مَا رَزَقْتَنَا) tak keh ley to agar Allah ne unki taqdeer mein aulad rakhi hai to usko shaitan zarar na pahunchaeyga aur mana iske ye hain ke shuru karta hun main Allah Taala ke naam se, ya Allah! bacha ham ko shaitan se aur door rakh shaitan ko us aulad se jo to ham ko inayat farmaeyga.''"
3534,"Shoba ne hamein hadis bayan ki, neez ibne-Numair aur Abdur-Razzaq ne Sory se (aur Sory aur Shoba ( donon ne Mansoor se Jarir ki hadis ke ham mana riwayat ki, lekin Shoba ki hadis mein Allah ke naam se ka zikr nahi, aur Sory se riwayat ki hui Abdur-Razzaq ki riwayat mein Allah ke naam se (ka jumla ( hai. aur ibne-Numair ki riwayat mein hai : Mansoor ne kaha : mera khayal hai ke unhon-ne kaha : Allah ke naam se."
3535,"Sufiyan ne hamein ibne-Munkadir se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se suna wo keh rahe they, yahood kaha kartey they : agar koi shakhs apni biwi ke peechhey ki taraf se uski sharm gaah mein mujamiat karey to bachcha bhengaa ( paida ( hoga. is par (ye aayat ( nazil hui : tumhari auratein tumhari kheti hain, so apni kheti mein aao jis taraf se chaho."
3536,"abu-Hazim ne Muhammad-bin Munkadir se, unhon-ne Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke yahood kaha kartey they : jab aurat ke peechhey ki taraf se uski sharmgah mein mubashrat ki jaey, phir wo haamla ho to uska bachcha bhenga hoga. kaha : is par (ye aayat ( nazil ki gaee : tumhari auratein tumhari kheti hain, so jis taraf se chaho apni kheti mein aao."
3537,"Qutaiba-bin-Saeed ne kaha : hamein abu-Awana ne hadis bayan ki. Abdul-Waris bin Abdus-Samad ne kaha : mujhey mere walid ne mere dada hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Ayub se riwayat ki Muhammad-bin-Musanna ne kaha : hamein Abdur-Rehman ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : hamein Sufiyan ne hadis sunai. Ubaidullah bin Sad , Harun bin-Abdullah aur abu-Ma'n Raqashi ne kaha : hamein Wahab bin Jarir ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : hamein mere walid ne hadis sunai, unhon-ne kaha : maine Nauman bin Rashid se suna, wo Zohri se riwayat kar rahe they. Sulaiman-bin Saeed ne kaha : hamein Mu-alla bin Asad ne hadis sunai, unhon-ne kaha : hamein Abdul-Azeez bin Mukhtar ne Sehal bin abi Saleh se hadis sunai, un sab ( abu-Awana , Ayub , Shoba , Sufiyan , Zohri aur Suhel bin abi Saleh ( ne Muhammad-bin Munkadir se, unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se yahi hadis bayan ki, Zohri se riwayat ki hui Nauman (bin Rashid ki hadis mein unke shagird Jarir ne) izafa kya : agar chahey to munh ke bal aur agar chahey to iske baghair ( kisi aur haiyat mein) , lekin ye aik hi dhakney (ki jagah , yani qubul (agley hissey)) mein ho."
3538,"Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Shoba ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : maine Qatada se suna wo Zarara-bin-Ufa se hadis bayan kar rahe they, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, aap ne farmaya : jab koi aurat (bila uzr) apne shauhar ke bistar ko chhod kar raat guzarti hai, to Farishtey iske subah karne tak is par laanat bhejtey rahtey hain."
3539,"Khalid-bin Haris ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne isi sanad ke sath yahi hadis bayan ki, aur kaha : yahan tak ke wo (iske bistar par) lot aaey."
3540,"Yazeed bin kaisaan ne abu-Hazim se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya is zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai! koi mard nahi jo apni biwi ko iske bistar ki taraf bulaey aur wo inkar karey magar wo jo aasman mein hai us se naraz rehta hai yahan tak ke wo ( shauhar (us se razi ho jaey."
3541,"Aamash ne abu-Hazim se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab mard apni biwi ko apne bistar par bulaey, wo na aaey aur wo ( shauhar (us par narazagi ki haalat mein raat guzaarey to iske subah karne tak Farishtey us aurat par laanat kartey rehtey hain."
3542,"Marwan bin Muawiya ne Umar-bin Hamza umri se hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Abdur-Rehman bin Sad ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : maine Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se suna wo keh rahe they : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : qiyamat ke din , Allah ke yahan logon mein martabey ke eitibaar se badtareen wo aadmi hoga jo apni biwi ke paas khilwat mein jata hai aur wo uske paas khilwat mein aati hai phir wo (aadmi) iska raaz afsha kar deta hai."
3543,"Muhammad-bin-Ubaidullah bin Numer aur abu-Kuraib ne kaha : hamein abu-Usama ne Umar-bin Hamza se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Abdur-Rehman bin Sad se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) se suna wo keh rahe they, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : bila shubah qiyamat ke din Allah ke yahan amanat ke hawale se sabse badey (sangin) maamlat mein se us aadmi (ka mamla) hoga jo tanhaai mein biwi ke paas jaey aur wo uske paas aaey, phir wo us ( biwi (ka raaz afsha kar de. ibne-Numair ne kaha : sabse bada (sangeen) mamla. (ye badi khayanat hai.)"
3544,"Rabee ne Muhammad-bin-Yahyaa bin Hibban se khabar di, unhon-ne ibne-Muhaireez se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : main aur abu-Sarma Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan hazir huey, abu-Sarma ne unse sawal kya aur kaha : abu-Saeed! kya aap ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko azl ka zikr kartey huey suna? unhon-ne kaha : haan, ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath bani-mustaliq ke khilaf jang ki aur Arab ki chunida auratein bataur ghaneemat hasil kin, hamein (apni aurton se) door rahtey huey kafi muddat ho chuki thi, aur ham (un aurton ke) fidye ki bhi raghbat rakhtey they, ham ne irada kya ke (un aurton se) fayda uthayen aur azl kar lein, ham ne kaha : ham ye kaam karein bhi aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hamarey darmyan maujood hon to unse sawal bhi na karein! chunanche ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se malum kya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : agar tum ( azl ( na bhi karo to tumhen koi nuqsan nahi hoga kyonke Allah ne qiyamat ke din tak ( paida ( honey wali jis jaan ki paidaaish likh di hai, wo zaroor paida hogi."
3545,"Musa-bin-Aqba ne Muhammad-bin-Yahya bin hibban se isi sanad ke sath Rabe ki hadis ke ham-mana hadis bayan ki, magar unhon-ne kaha : Allah ne (pahley hi ( likh diya hai ke wo qiyamat ke din tak kis ko paida karne wala hai."
3546,"Zohri ne ibne-Muhaireez se aur unhon-ne Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne un ( ibne-Muhaireez) ko khabar di, hamein laundiyaan hasil huin to (unke saath) ham azl kartey they, phir ham ne iske barey mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha to aap ne hamein farmaya : (kya ( tum aisa kartey ho? tum aisa kartey ho? ( waqei ( tum aisa kartey ho? koi jaan nahi jo qiyamat tak paida honey wali ho magar wo paida ho kar rahegi."
3547,"Bishr-bin-Mufazzal ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne Anas-bin-Sirin se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Mabad-bin-Sirin se, unhon-ne Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, ( Anas-bin-Sirin ne) kaha : maine un ( Mabad ( se puchha : aap ne ye Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) se khud suna hai? unhon-ne kaha : haan ! unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tumhen is baat ka koi nuqsan nahi ke tum (aisa) na karo, ye to sirf taqdeer hai (jo tum azl karo ya na karo, har sura poori ho kar rahegi.)"
3548,"Muhammad-bin-Jafar, Khalid-bin-Haaris, Abdur-Rehman-bin-Mehdi aur Bahaz, sab ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne Anas-bin-Sirin se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki, magar unki hadis mein (is tarah) hai : unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, aap ne azl ke barey mein farmaya : (is mein) koi harj nahi ke tum ye kaam na karo, ye to bas taqdeer (ka mamla) hai. Behaz ki riwayat mein hai, Shoba ne kaha : maine unse puchha : kya aap ne ye hadis abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) se sunii? unhon-ne kaha : haan."
3549,"Ayub ne hamein Muhammad (bin-Sirin ( se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Abdur-Rehman-bin-Bishr-bin-Masood se riwayat ki, usey peechhey Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) tak le gaey ( unse riwayat ki), unhon-ne kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se azl ke barey mein sawal kiya gaya to aap ne farmaya : tum par koi harj nahi ke tum ye kaam na karo, ye to bas taqdeer (ka mamla ( hai. Muhammad (bin-Sirin ( ne kaha : Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka qaul : is baat ka tum par koi harj nahi manaahii ke zyada qareeb hai."
3550,"Muaaz-bin-Muaaz ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Ibne-Aun ne Muhammad (bin-Sirin ( se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Abdur-Rehman-bin-Bishr-Ansari se riwayat ki, aur is hadis ko peechhey le gaey aur usey Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf mansub kiya, unhon-ne kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas azl ka tazkira kiya gaya, to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : (is se) tumhara maqsad kya hai? sahaba kiram (Raziallahu anhu) ne jawab diya : kisi aadmi ki biwi hai) bachchey ko) doodh pilaa rahi hoti hai, wo us se mubashrat karta hai aur na-pasand karta hai ke wo us se haamla ho. aur kisi shakhs ki londi hai wo us se mubashrat karta hai aur na-pasand karta hai ke wo us se haamla ho. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : koi harj nahi ke tum aisa na karo, ye ( bachchey ka paida hona ya na hona ( to taqdeer ka mamla hai. Ibne-Aun ne kaha : maine ye hadis Hasan ( Basri) ko sunai to unhon-ne kaha : Allah ki qism ! ye to maano daant hai."
3551,"Hammad-bin-Zaid ne Ibne-Aun se hadis bayan ki, kaha : maine Hammad (bin-Sirin ( ko Ibrahim ke waastey se Abdur-Rehman-bin-Bishr ki hadis , yani azl ki hadis sunai to unhon-ne kaha : Abdur-Rehman-bin-Bishr ne khud mujhey bhi ye hadis bayan ki."
3552,"Hisham ne hamein Muhammad (bin-Sirin) se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Mabad-bin-Sirin se riwayat ki, kaha : ham ne Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) se arz ki, kya aap ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko azl ke barey mein kuchh farmatey huey sunaa? unhon-ne kaha : haan. aagey unhon-ne (ye to taqdeer hai) tak Ibne-Aun ki hadis ke ham mana hadis bayan ki."
3553,"Qaza' ne Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney azl ka zikr kiya gaya to aap ne farmaya : tum mein se koi shakhs aisa kyon karta hai? aap ne ye nahi farmaya : tum mein se koi aisa na kare. haqiqat ye hai paida honey wali koi jaan nahi magar Allah usey paida karne wala hai. (wo usey zaroor paida karega .)"
3554,"Abdullah-bin-Wahab ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : mujhey Muawiya-bin-Saleh ne Ali-bin-abu-Talha se khabar di, unhon-ne abu-waddak se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon ( abu-wadaak ( ne unse suna, wo keh rahe they : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se azl ke barey mein sawal kiya gaya, aap ne farmaya : har pani ( mani ke qatrey ( se bachcha paida nahi hota, aur jab Allah Taala kisi cheez ko paida karne ka irada farma leta hai to usey koi cheez rok nahi sakti."
3555,"Zaid-bin-Hubab ne Muawiya se, baqi bachi isi sanad ke sath Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi hadis ki manind (tarah) hadis bayan ki."
3556,"abu-Zubair ne hamein Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se khabar di ke aik aadmi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaya, aur kaha : meri aik londi hai, wahi hamari khaadima hai aur wahi hamarey liye pani laney wali bhi hai. aur main us se mujamiat (sambhog) bhi karta hun. mein na-pasand karta hun ke wo haamla ho. to aap ne farmaya : agar tum chaho to us se azl kar liya karo, ( lekin) ye baat yaqeeni hai ke jo bachcha uske liye muqaddar mein likha gaya hai wo aa kar rahega. wo shakhs ( chand din) ruka , phir aap ki khidmat mein hazir hua, aur kaha : wo londi haamla ho gaee hai. to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : maine tumhen bata diya tha ke jo uske liye muqaddar kiya gaya hai wo aa kar rahega."
3557,"Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne hamein Saeed-bin-Hassan se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Urwa-bin-ayaaz se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : aik aadmi ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se malum kiya, aur kaha : mere paas meri aik londi hai, main us se azl karta hun. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : be-shak ye ( azl ( aisi kisi cheez ko nahi rok sakta jiska Allah ne irada kiya ho. kaha : wo shakhs (dobara ( haazire-khidmat hua aur kehney laga : Allah ke rasool ! wo londi jiska maine aap se zikr kiya tha, haamla ho gaee hai. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : main Allah ka banda aur rasool hun. (main jo kehta hun Allah ki taraf se kehta hoon.)"
3558,"abu-Ahmed zubairii ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Makka ke qissaa sunaaney waley Saeed-bin-Hassan ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : mujhey Urwa-bin-ayaaz-bin-Adii-bin-khiyaar-naufalii ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se khabar di, unhon-ne kaha : aik aadmi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua. ( aagey ( Sufiyan ki hadis ke ham mana. ( hai)"
3559,"hamein abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba aur Ishaq-bin-Ibrahim ne hadis bayan ki, ( unhon-ne kaha ( hamein Sufiyan ne Amr se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Ata se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : ham azl kartey they jabke Quraan nazil ho raha hota tha. Ishaq ne izafa kiya : Sufiyan ne kaha : agar ye aisi cheez hoti jis se mana kiya jana ( zaroori ( hota to Quraan hamein ( zaroor ( is se mana karta."
3560,"Maaqil ne hamein Ata se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they : ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ahad mein azl kiya kartey they."
3561,"abu-Zubair ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamaney mein azl kartey they. ye baat Allah ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko pahunchi to aap ne hamein mana nahi farmaya."
3562,"Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Shoba ne Yazeed-bin-khumair se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Abdur-Rehman-bin-Juber se suna wo apne walid ( Jubair-bin-Nufair ( se hadis bayan kar rahe they, unhon-ne abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khemey ke darwazey par khadi aik poorey dinon ki haamla aurat ( londi (ke paas se guzrey, aap ne farmaya : shayad wo ( uska Malik ( chahta hai ke uske sath mujamiat (sambhog) karey? sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ji haan , to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : maine irada kiya ke is par aisi laanat bhejoon jo uski qabr mein iske sath jaey. aisa kaam karne wala kaisey is ( tarah ke bachchey ( ko waaris banaeyga , jabke wo ( waaris banaanaa ( uske liye halal nahi. wo kaisey us se khidmat lega ( usey ghulam banaeyga ? ( jabke (is bachchey ke pet mein honey ke doran mein uski maan se mubashrat karne ki bina par is bachchey / bachchii ko ghulam / kaneez banaanaa ( uske liye halal nahi."
3563,Yazid-bin-Harun aur Abu-Dawud ne Shoba se isi sanad ke sath ye hadis bayan ki.
3564,"judaama ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna ke farmatey they : maine chaha ke gheelaa (doodh pilaaney wali aouret se sambhog) se mana kar dun phir mujhey yad aaya ke Rome (mojooda Itly) aur Faaris gheelaa kartey hain aur unki aulad ko nuksaan nahi hota. jahan tak Khalaf ka talluq hai to unhon-ne kaha : juzaama Asadiya se riwayat hai, Muslim ne farmaya ke judaama be nuqta ke daal se sahi hai."
3565,"Ubaidullah-bin-Saeed aur Muhammad-bin-abi-Umar ne hamein hadis bayan ki, un donon ne kaha : hamein muqri ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Saeed-bin-abi-Ayub ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : mujhey abu-Aswad ne Urwa se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se, unhon-ne Ukasha (Raziallahu anhu) ki behan judaama-binte-Wahab (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : main logon ki maujoodgii mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hui, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farma rahe they : maine irada kiya tha ke gheelaa ( doodh pilaaney wali biwi ke sath mubashrat karne) se mana kar dun, phir maine Rome (mojooda Itly) aur Faaris (ke logon ke barey ( mein dekha ( sochaa , ghaur kiya ( to wo apne bachchon (ki doodh pilaaney wali maaon ( se gheelaa kartey hain aur ye unke bachchon ko kuchh nuqsan nahi pahunchata. phir sahaba ne aap se azl ke barey mein puchha to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ye saaf tour per zinda qaber mein dafan karna hai. Ubaidullah ne muqrii se riwayat ki hui apni hadis mein izafa kiya : aur yahi hai : zinda qaber mein dafan ki gaee ladki se (qiyamat ke din) puchha jaeyga."
3566,"Yahya-bin-Ayub ne hamein Muhammad-bin-Abdur-Rehman-bin-naufal qarshii se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Urwa se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se, unhon-ne judaama-binte-Wahab Asadiya (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna. aagey azl aur gheelaa ke barey mein Saeed-bin-abu-Ayyoob ki hadis ki tarah bayan kiya. lekin unhon-ne ( gheelaa ke bajaey) gheeyal kaha ( mana wahi hain. ("
3567,"Muhammad-bin-Abdullah-bin-Numair aur Zuhair-bin-Harab ne. padhi. alfaz ibne-Numair ke hain. padhi. hadis bayan ki, donon ne kaha : hamein Abdullah-bin-Yazeed Maqbari ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Hewa ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : mujhey Ayash-bin-Abbas ne hadis sunai, unhein abu-Nazar ne Aamir-bin-Sad se hadis bayan ki ke Usama-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ne unke walid Sad-bin-abi-Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) ko khabar di ke aik aadmi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur kaha : main apni biwi se azl karta hun, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha : tum aisa kyon kartey ho? us ne jawab diya : main iske bachchey ya iske bachchon par) jinhein wo doodh pilaa rahi hoti hai) shafqat karta hun (ke unhein koi nuqsan na ho) to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : agar ye nuqsan deh hota to Faaris aur Rome (mojooda Itly) (ke bachchon ( ko nuqsan deta. Zuhair ne apni riwayat mein kaha : agar ye ( azl ( is wjah se hai to ( iski zarurat ( nahi, is (amal ( ne Faaris aur Rome (mojooda Itly) (ke bachchon ( ko koi nuqsan nahi pahunchaya."
